high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink
Pick up the knife that's in front of you
Turn around and walk over to the wooden stool on your left
Slice up the tomato that's on the table
Turn around and go back to the sink
Place the knife into the sink
Turn around and go back over to the tomato you just sliced
Pick up a tomato slice from the table
Turn back around and go back to the sink
Put the tomato slice into the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up
Turn to your right and look at the microwave
Place the tomato slice into the left side of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Cut up a tomato, heat the sliced tomato piece

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the counter and go to the right to face the sink.
Pick the knife up from off of the sink.
Turn around, walk towards the counter, and face the brown stool.
Cut the tomato on the counter in to several slices.
Turn around and go straight to face the sink.
Place the knife in to the sink.
Turn around and walk straight towards the brown stool next to the counter.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the counter.
Turn around and walk back towards the sink.
Place the tomato slice in to the sink, run some water over it, turn the water off, and pick up the tomato slice.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the tomato slice inside, and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the slice of tomato in to the microwave on the counter.

high_descs: Walk to the opposite corner of the room and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to the stool in front of the counter and face the tomato on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn around and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to face the tomato on the counter in front of the stool.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to face the sink.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink and remove it.
Turn to the right to face the microwave on the counter.
Place the slice of tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: TO cut a tomato, clean it, plus place it into the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen sink on the other side of the room
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the front sill of the sink.
Carry the knife to the counter in the middle of the kitchen.
Slice up the tomato
Take the knife back to the sink.
Set the knife inside the sink.
Go back to the center table where the tomato is.
Take the rightmost end of the tomato that has been sliced toward the kitchen sink.
Set the end of the tomato inside the sink.
Turn the water on at the sink then let the water drain from the sink.
Pick up the slice from the sink.
Go to the microwave, put the slice of tomato inside the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Get a knife, cut up a tomato, take a piece of the tomato, wash it. Put it in the microwave shut the door.
